s.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1620%2C969 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=554%2C331, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1108%2C662 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1662%2C994 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=554%2C331, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1108%2C662 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1662%2C994 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C371, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1240%2C741 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1860%2C1112 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C371, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1240%2C741 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1860%2C1112 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=408%2C244, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=816%2C488 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C732 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1632%2C976 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=408%2C244, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=816%2C488 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C732 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1632%2C976 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C332, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C665 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C997 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C332, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C665 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C997 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-417806 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--full no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/Robert_Smith-ce7185b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C371\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Cyclist sprinting on a road bike in winter\" title=\"Cyclist sprinting on a road bike in winter\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture>\n</div>\n<div class=\"caption-hold\">\n<figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> HIIT workouts can take place indoors or outdoors, though the turbo trainer is most convenient.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Robert Smith/Immediate Media</i></span>\n</div>\n<h2>Indoors or outdoors?<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br></span>\n</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While HIIT training can be done both <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/fitness-and-training/indoor-vs-outdoor-cycle-training/\">indoors or outdoors</a>, all the coaches we spoke to leaned towards an indoor setting on a turbo trainer or <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/indoor-bikes/\">smart bike</a>.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“I personally prefer to do it indoors,” says Wattbike’s Nichols. “It’s convenient, setup ready to go and there’s no time-wasting. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Doing it outdoors can negate the time effectiveness of HIIT.”</span></p>\n<p>The latest <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-indoor-cycling-apps/\">indoor cycling apps</a> offer structured <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/fitness-and-training/best-workouts-training-plans-zwift/\">workouts and training plans</a>, many of which include HIIT-style interval sessions. The <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-smart-trainer/\">best smart trainers</a> can control the resistance for each interval, ensuring you hit the numbers required to <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/fitness-and-training/how-to-get-fit-fast/\">get fit fast</a>.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you do opt to train outside, Bottrill recommends planning a circuit that is either flat or uphill.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“You don’t want it to be too undulating and you want to control the environment,” he says. “That’s where a hill comes good – you can ascend a climb that’s 3-4 minutes and then recover on the descent.”</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rowe adds that it’s also possible to turn your commute into a HIIT workout, albeit an unstructured fartlek-style session: “</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Maybe as part of your commute, you could sprint to a sign post and do seemingly random efforts like that.”</span></p>\n<p>Of course, as with any high-intensity ride outside, make sure you are paying full attention to your surroundings at all times.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/fitness-and-training/how-to-take-ftp-test-zwift/\">How to take an FTP or ramp test on Zwift</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>How can I include HIIT in my training plan?</h2>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--full\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% * (3777 / 6714));\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C169, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C338 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C506 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C675 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C169, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C338 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C506 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C675 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=355%2C200, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=710%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/11/Vitus-and-Genesis-road-bikes_Robert-Smith-2019_road_female-59a5a8f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1065%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/1